<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Ulrich Harb, Vogt zu Burgheim, und Ludwig VII. von Wittelsbach, Herzog von Bayern-Ingolstadt</head><p>Der Rat kündigt Hans Göldlein, Diener der Stadt, wegen der gefangenen Armleute zu Burgsalach von Hans Stark und Peter Behaim, Bürger zu Nürnberg, und ihrer beschlagnahmten Habe an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_327" id="162v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_327_r2l1"><expan>Vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>harb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vogt cʒu Burkheym </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_327_r2l2"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> vogt . Als vvır euch nehſt <expan>geſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_327_r2l3">von hanſen Starken . vnd peter Beheyms <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_327_r2l4">burgere 
<del rend="strikethrough">Ar </del> vnd <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> Armlewte wegen cʒu Salach </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_327_r2l5">als den Jr habe <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> . etlich gefangen cʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_327_r2l6">ew gen Burkhaym braht ſein worden . <expan>Dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_327_r2l7">ſenden vvir cʒu euch hanſen Göldlein <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_327_r2l8">diener mit euch dauon cʒu Reden . vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_327_r2l9"><expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>do<ex>min</ex>ıca</expan> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>Mich<ex>aelis</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter"><ab facs="#facs_327_r2l10">Hercʒog <expan>Ludwyg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>ſı<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_327_r2l11"><expan>mutat<ex>is</ex></expan> <expan>mutand<ex>is</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_327" id="162v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>Harb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, vogt czu Burkheym</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> vogt, als wir euch nehst
                                <expan>geschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von Hansen Starken und Peter Beheyms,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> burgere, und
                            <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> armlewte wegen czu Salach, als den ir habe
                                <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan>, etlich gefangen czu ew gen Burkhaym
                        braht sein worden. <expan>Dar<ex>umb</ex></expan> senden wir czu euch Hansen
                        Göldlein <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener, mit euch davon czu reden.
                        Und <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>do<ex>min</ex>ica</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Mich<ex>aelis</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab>Herczog <expan>Ludwyg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>
<expan>mutat<ex>is</ex></expan>
<expan>mutand<ex>is</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
